description: By supporting this project, you are helping Fun Games Shop regain the production costs and to rebuild their hobby and game shop in Kyiv, Ukraine. https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/fungamesshop/catapult-feud-ukraine-edition

Many of you have inquired about my awesome map. Turns out it's a Ukrainian made company call @enjoythewood_ .
